How to Obtain the Data:
Dataset: IMDB Dataset of 50,000 Movie Reviews
Source: Kaggle - IMDB Dataset of 50K Movie Reviews
Access using this link: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/lakshmi25npathi/imdb-dataset-of-50k-movie-reviews?select=IMDB+Dataset.csv
Then, click the download button in the upper-right corner and download the dataset as zip. Then, open the dataset in Downloads on the computer.
